[[Tinta Lines]] was a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] shipping corporation. It was owned by the [[Tinta (family)|Tinta family]]. The owner of Tinta Lines hired [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] to guard his daughter, [[Siolle Tinta]], aboard the luxury cruiser ''[[Tinta Rainbow]]''. While aboard the ship, Corran learned cuisine from [[Chef/Legends|Chef]] [[Chid]].

